# Data Mart (Star Schema)

This folder contains the SQL scripts for the **analytical data mart layer**.

The data mart is modeled as a **star schema** and is optimized for reporting
and BI tools.

It includes:
- Dimension tables (DIM)
- Fact tables (FACT)

The mart layer is built from the Data Vault core and provides
a simplified, performance-optimized view of the data for analytics
and visualization.
